<i>verb</i>: 구박하다 [구바카다], 가학하다 [가하카다] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>구박하다 [구바카다]</dt><br>
<dd>be hard on; ill-treat; molest</dd><br>
<dd>못 견딜 정도로 매우 심하게 괴롭히다.</dd><br>
<dd>To severely abuse someone to such a degree that it is hard to bear.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>가학하다 [가하카다]</dt><br>
<dd>mistreat; ill-treat</dd><br>
<dd>심하고 잔인하게 괴롭히다.</dd><br>
<dd>To harass terribly and cruelly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>